PN,43101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1778217988
OL,3,CGroup who supplied #600k of cocaine
OL,4,Csentenced to 36 years
OL,6,FFive men who ran a drugs operation
OL,7,Fsupplying more than half a million
OL,8,Fpounds-worth of cocaine in
OL,9,FGloucestershire have been jailed for a
OL,10,Ftotal of 36 years and 8 months.
OL,12,FJordan Ireland, Ashley Booth, Scott
OL,13,FCapstick, Brian Dennis and James
OL,14,FBlandford all pled guilty to
OL,15,Fconspiracy to supply cocaine after an
OL,16,Finvestigation by Gloucestershire
OL,17,FPolice's Serious Organised Crime Unit.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
