FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1778217988
OL,3,CGroup who supplied #600k of cocaine
OL,4,Csentenced to 36 years
OL,6,FIreland has been handed a sentence of
OL,7,F11 years 8 months, Blandford 8 years 3
OL,8,Fmonths, Booth 7 years 1 month, Dennis
OL,9,F6 years 4 months and Capstick 3 years
OL,10,F4 months.
OL,12,FThe group was found to have sent or
OL,13,Fowed at least #600,000 to their
OL,14,Fsuppliers and supplied at least 25
OL,15,Fkilograms of the Class A drug to the
OL,16,Fcounty since February 2023.
OL,18,FVideos recovered after phones were
OL,19,Fseized showed the group bulking out
OL,20,Fhigh-purity cocaine with anaesthetics
OL,21,Flike benzocaine in Ireland's kitchen.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
