FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1778217988
OL,3,CGroup who supplied #600k of cocaine
OL,4,Csentenced to 36 years
OL,6,FDCI Matt Philips of the
OL,7,FGloucestershire Police Serious
OL,8,FOrganised Crime Unit said: "They sent
OL,9,For owed at least #600,00 to their
OL,10,Fupstream suppliers and evidence of at
OL,11,Fleast 25 kilos of class A drugs coming
OL,12,Finto the county of Gloucestershire."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
