FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1778217988
OL,3,CGroup who supplied #600k of cocaine
OL,4,Csentenced to 36 years
OL,6,F"They had somebody who created the
OL,7,Fmould for them who had access to a
OL,8,Fhydraulic press in a car garage... We
OL,9,Fcan see from mobile phone evidence
OL,10,Fthat they also had a token system they
OL,11,Fused with their cash couriers, to make
OL,12,Fsure they were handing over money to
OL,13,Fthe right people, because sometimes
OL,14,Fthey were handing over bags with
OL,15,Fhundreds of thousands of pounds in."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
