OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1778217988
OL,3,CGroup who supplied #600k of cocaine
OL,4,Csentenced to 36 years
OL,6,F"They would sell drugs to a network of
OL,7,Fsub-dealers, so they would potentially
OL,8,Fbuy in one or two kilos of quite high-
OL,9,Fpurity cocaine. They would adulterate
OL,10,Fit with something like benzocaine to
OL,11,Fbulk it out and increase their profit
OL,12,Fmargins, and then they would sell it
OL,13,Fon to sub-dealers in half-kilo,
OL,14,Fquarter-kilo amounts."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
