PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1778217988
OL,3,CGroup who supplied #600k of cocaine
OL,4,Csentenced to 36 years
OL,6,FHe went on to say: "It's a real
OL,7,Fsuccess and it's testament to the hard
OL,8,Fwork and dedication not just from the
OL,9,Fsurvellance officers but the rest of
OL,10,Fthe investigation team that piece all
OL,11,Fthe evidence together and show a
OL,12,Freally compelling case to the court."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
